            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides a solar hydrogen-electricity co-production energy storage system and method. Relates to the technical field of fuel production power generation. According to the invention, the heat in the process of producing fuel by solar energy is recycled and used for thermodynamic cycle power generation, and the generated power is used for the power consumption equipment in the system, so that the solar energy utilization efficiency can be improved; by arranging the medium-high temperature solid storage tank, continuous production of fuel and electricity can be achieved; and by coupling the system with photovoltaic energy, electric power can be stored when renewable energy is excessive, and can be discharged when the load of the power grid is relatively high, so that an energy storage function is realized."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本公开提供一种太阳能氢‑电联产储能系统及方法；涉及燃料生产发电技术领域。本公开通过回收利用太阳能生产燃料过程中的热量并用于热力循环发电，以及将所产生的电力用于系统中的耗电设备，可以提高太阳能利用效率；通过设置中高温固体储罐，可以实现燃料与电的连续生产；通过将系统与光伏能源相耦合，还可以在可再生能源过剩时将电力储存，并在电网负荷较高时放出，从而实现储能功能。"
                }
